# AI sync working files are committed; nothing to ignore there

# resume-source.docx is a DERIVED artifact (gitignored). As of v2.23 it
# is built from scratch by scripts/build-resume.py from two tracked,
# diffable text sources — resume-static.yml + projects.yml — so the
# resume is fully reproducible without committing a binary (and without
# the Office-metadata-privacy concern that kept it local since v2.12).
# The canonical published artifact is resume.pdf (LibreOffice converts
# the freshly-built docx).
*.docx
__pycache__/
